# Product Images Upload Directory

This directory contains uploaded product images.

## Structure
- Original images are stored here directly
- Thumbnails are generated automatically (if implemented)

## Notes
- Maximum file size: 10MB
- Allowed formats: JPG, JPEG, PNG, GIF, WEBP
- Images are renamed with unique identifiers to prevent conflicts

## Security
- PHP execution is disabled in this directory via .htaccess
- Direct access to files is allowed for image display
